# Description
# -----------
#
#  Completion script for the optirun command from bumblebee
#  (https://github.com/Bumblebee-Project/Bumblebee).
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authors
# -------
#
#  * Christophe-Marie Duquesne <chm.duquesne@gmail.com>
#
